: \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 355, \"end\": 369, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lauren_Scruggs\", \"score\": 0.9999934662759814, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lauren Scruggs\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lauren_Scruggs\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lauren_Scruggs\"}, {\"begin\": 379, \"end\": 392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9978215821636849, \"rank\": 0.0020054933282927017, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 452, \"end\": 458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.808424249660786, \"rank\": 0.2341896878483484, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 545, \"end\": 550, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9764354151497294, \"rank\": 0.01818558426061912, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 553, \"end\": 562, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Koki_Kano\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Koki Kano\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Koki_Kano\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Koki_Kano\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kiefer, who was the first American to win an Olympic foil gold when she triumphed three years ago in Tokyo, retained the title with a comfortable 15-6 victory over her younger teammate Scruggs in the final at the stunning Grand Palais venue.\", \"from\": 588, \"to\": 829, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 614, \"end\": 622, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.997688587222632, \"rank\": 0.0023162111003192415, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 689, \"end\": 694, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999999399071857, \"rank\": 5.994327236191409e-08, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's insane,\\\" said 30-year-old\\u00a0Kiefer, whose mother Teresa traces her roots to Tagum City in\\u00a0Davao del Norte, Philippines.\", \"from\": 831, \"to\": 954, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 911, \"end\": 921, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tagum\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tagum City\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tagum\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tagum\"}, {\"begin\": 925, \"end\": 940, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Davao_del_Norte\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.282294553353336e-19, \"text\": \"Davao del Norte\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Davao_del_Norte\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Davao_del_Norte\"}, {\"begin\": 942, \"end\": 953, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.5513226036606029, \"rank\": 0.8017336722944292, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"These three years have been so short and so long at the same time.\", \"from\": 955, \"to\": 1022, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Every day it's been a freaking battle and I have so many people to thank for helping me get here on this day, in this moment.\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1148, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's absolutely historical,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1190, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Lauren fenced amazing this whole season and she deserves all this respect.\\\"\", \"from\": 1191, \"to\": 1267, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Scruggs, 21, stunned Italian favorite Arianna Errigo in the quarterfinals to reach the Olympic final at the first attempt.\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1391, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1290, \"end\": 1297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"score\": 0.7726463399033024, \"rank\": 0.26309828512823724, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1307, \"end\": 1321, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arianna_Errigo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Arianna Errigo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arianna_Errigo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arianna_Errigo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am super happy, you know,\\\" said a tearful Scruggs, the first Black American fencer to win an Olympic medal in a women's individual event.\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1533, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1457, \"end\": 1462, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/African_Americans\", \"score\": 0.9815366880797418, \"rank\": 0.018810486237182913, \"text\": \"Black\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/African_Americans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/African_Americans\"}, {\"begin\": 1463, \"e